<div id="help_puzzle_modal" class="modal hide fade">
    <div class="modal-header">
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">&times;</button>
        <h2 class="title1">Welcome to DCBD Puzzle Game</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="modal-body">
        <h3>How to play: </h3>
        <p>Click and drag every pieces to its designated area until all of the puzzle pieces are in place.</p>
        
        <h3>Controls: </h3>
        
        <p>Move: </p>
        <p> - Click & Drag</p>
        
        <p>Rotate: </p>
        <p> - DoubleClick</p>
        
        <p>Flip along X-axis: </p>
        <p> - DoubleClick & [alt]Key</p>
        <p> - Right Mouse Button</p>
        
        <p>Flip along Y-axis: </p>
        <p> - DoubleClick & [shift]Key</p>
        <p> - Middle Mouse Button</p>
    </div>

    <div class="modal-footer">
        <button class="art-button" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
    </div>
</div>